snippet.title: UTOPIA SYNDROME - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Info: https://www.utopiasyndrome.com/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/955020/Utopia_Syndrome/
About: Unique visual style and top-down gaming perspective. The intersection of destinies, mysterious parallel storylines in a horror, mystic and world exploration adventure game. Click, read and interact, gather inventory items, notes and clues to solve puzzles to progress further. Immerse yourself in the dark corners of Utopia world to remember your past, present and future.
